---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'Best Free Sitemap Generator — 2025 Comparison of Top Tools';
const description = 'Compare the best free sitemap generators in 2025: AI Sitemap Generator vs Screaming Frog, AIOSEO, xml-sitemaps.com, and Google Search Console. Features, pricing, and limitations.';

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "Best Free Sitemap Generator — 2025 Comparison",
  "description": description,
  "author": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "AI Sitemap Generator" },
  "publisher": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "AI Sitemap Generator",
    "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": "https://ai-sitemap-generator.pages.dev/favicon.svg" }
  },
  "datePublished": "2025-01-10",
  "dateModified": "2025-05-17",
  "mainEntityOfPage": "https://ai-sitemap-generator.pages.dev/compare/sitemap-generator-alternatives"
};
---

<BaseLayout {title} {description}>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(jsonLd)} />
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[var(--color-background)] text-[var(--color-foreground)]">
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 backdrop-blur-xl bg-[var(--color-background)]/80 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]/60 px-4 sm:px-6 py-3.5">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M15 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-4"/><polyline points="10 17 15 12 10 7"/><line x1="15" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/></svg>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">AI Sitemap Generator</span>
          <span class="sm:hidden">SitemapGen</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/tools/sitemap" class="text-sm font-medium bg-[var(--color-primary)] text-white px-4 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
          Launch Tool
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-4">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-[var(--color-foreground)] transition-colors">Home</a>
          <span class="mx-2">/</span>
          <a href="/compare/sitemap-generator-alternatives" class="hover:text-[var(--color-foreground)] transition-colors">Compare</a>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4">Best Free Sitemap Generator — 2025 Comparison</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]">How the top sitemap tools stack up: features, pricing, and which one is right for you.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose-container space-y-8 text-[var(--color-foreground)] leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]">Choosing the right XML sitemap generator online can save you hours and improve your SEO results. Here's an honest comparison of the most popular options — including our own tool — so you can pick the best fit for your needs.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Feature Comparison</h2>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm min-w-[600px]">
              <thead>
                <tr class="bg-[var(--color-secondary)]">
                  <th class="text-left p-4 font-semibold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Feature</th>
                  <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold text-[var(--color-primary)]">AI Sitemap Gen</th>
                  <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Screaming Frog</th>
                  <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">AIOSEO</th>
                  <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">xml-sitemaps</th>
                  <th class="text-center p-4 font-semibold text-[var(--color-foreground)]">GSC</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]">
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M15 9h-.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0-2.5 2.5v0a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-2.5 2.5H9"/></svg>
                    Price
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)] font-semibold">Free</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">$259/yr</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">$49.60/yr</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Freemium</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Free</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><path d="M19 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H9a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
                    Sign-up Required
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><path d="M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z"/></svg>
                    AI-Powered Insights
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">Yes (BYOK)</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/><path d="M11 8v6"/><path d="M8 11h6"/></svg>
                    SEO Issue Detection
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Limited</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Basic</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><path d="M6 3v12"/><path d="M18 9a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/><path d="M6 21a3 3 0 1 0 0-6 3 3 0 0 0 0 6z"/><path d="M15 6H9a3 3 0 0 0 0 6h6"/></svg>
                    Visual Site Tree
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
                    Works Online (No Install)
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3"/></svg>
                    Statistics Dashboard
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">Limited</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]">
                  <td class="p-4 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
                    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="shrink-0 text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                    Open Source
                  </td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center text-[var(--color-primary)]">Yes</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                  <td class="p-4 text-center">No</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Tool-by-Tool Breakdown</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-primary)]/30 bg-[var(--color-primary)]/5 p-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)]">AI Sitemap Generator</h3>
                <span class="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)]/20 text-[var(--color-primary)] font-medium">This Tool</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-3">A free, open-source SEO sitemap tool that runs entirely in the browser. No sign-up, no install, no limits. Unique features include AI-powered priority and changefreq suggestions (bring your own API key), a visual site tree, and comprehensive SEO issue detection — all at zero cost.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><strong class="text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Best for:</strong> Developers, SEO professionals, and site owners who want a fast, free tool with advanced analysis features.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)] mb-2">Screaming Frog SEO Spider</h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-3">A desktop application that's the industry standard for technical SEO audits. Extremely powerful with detailed crawling, but requires installation and the paid version ($259/year) for sites with more than 500 URLs. No AI features, no online usage.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><strong class="text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Best for:</strong> Professional SEO agencies doing deep technical audits on client sites.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)] mb-2">All in One SEO (AIOSEO)</h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-3">A WordPress plugin that auto-generates sitemaps. Convenient if your site runs on WordPress, but it's limited to that platform and requires a paid license for advanced features. No crawl analysis or visual site structure.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><strong class="text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Best for:</strong> WordPress site owners who want set-and-forget sitemap generation.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)] mb-2">xml-sitemaps.com</h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-3">One of the oldest online sitemap generators. The free version limits you to 500 pages and has no SEO analysis. The paid version unlocks more pages but still lacks issue detection or visual tools.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><strong class="text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Best for:</strong> Quick, simple sitemap generation for small sites.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-foreground)] mb-2">Google Search Console</h3>
              <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-3">Not a sitemap generator per se — you need to create the file elsewhere and submit it here. GSC provides indexation reports and error alerts, making it an essential companion to any sitemap tool. Free, but limited to Google and requires site verification.</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]"><strong class="text-[var(--color-foreground)]">Best for:</strong> Monitoring sitemap health and indexation status post-submission.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Bottom Line</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]">For most users — especially developers and site owners who want a quick, powerful solution without installing software or creating accounts — a free online sitemap generator with built-in SEO analysis offers the best value. Tools like Screaming Frog are excellent for professional audits, but overkill for everyday sitemap generation.</p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mt-4">The ideal workflow: generate your sitemap with our free tool, submit it via Google Search Console and Bing Webmaster Tools, and monitor indexation status in GSC. This combination gives you both generation and monitoring at zero cost.</p>
        </section>

        <div class="mt-12 p-8 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/10 to-purple-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Try It Free — No Sign-up Required</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] mb-6">Generate your sitemap in under a minute and see why it's the best free option.</p>
          <a href="/tools/sitemap" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-primary)] text-white font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
            Generate Your Sitemap
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 text-sm">
          <a href="/guide/how-to-create-sitemap" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">&larr; How to Create a Sitemap</a>
          <a href="/guide/sitemap-faq" class="text-[var(--color-primary)] hover:underline">Sitemap FAQ &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <footer class="border-t border-[var(--color-border)]/50 px-6 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)]">
        <span>&copy; 2025–2026 AI Sitemap Generator</span>
        <span>Built with Astro + Cloudflare</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
